{
  "stem": "1828.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she-- maybe it was because of that that we were well nourished and that we didn't suffer any malnutrition, really-- any signs of it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they'd buy eggs at-- at ridiculous prices, and always have something special for Shabbos, no matter what it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She became very inventive, and-- and imitating the former food by substitutes in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It-- we went on, and it was not-- we adjusted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my father had a daily [NON-ENGLISH], where he had a chavrusa, where he learned every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it-- we-- we were-- my sister had to stop her schooling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was ahead of me, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's older.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents enrolled her in a-- in a language school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She studied Spanish and English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we also used our time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There our parents arranged for someone to come in and teach us how to make artificial flowers out of leather, and all kinds of accessories.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And mother said, it's very important to know what to do when you need to earn for your bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even if you never know it-- need it, so you would still have it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we also prepared things that my parents learned from the first world, which didn't apply at all to the second one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They sewed coins and certain valuables into our lapels, and said to watch for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if the war breaks out and we have to leave, always remember that you have reserves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if you're very hungry or if you can save your life with it, use it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that, apparently, is what you could do in the-- during the world-- first world world war where it-- it didn't apply in our case.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and where are we now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At-- yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
